data.description: Come tour this quaint residence nestled within the desirable Planters Walk subdivision, just steps away from Ogden Park. This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, two inviting living areas, a cozy wood-burning fireplace, and a privately fenced backyard on over a quarter of an acre. The property further offers a spacious 20'x30' Spanish tile patio, ideal for both grilling and entertaining. Hardwood laminate flooring throughout, with carpeting throughout the back bedrooms for added comfort. Minutes away from Mayfair shopping and dining scene, and a quick ten-minute drive to 'toes in the sand' of Wrightsville Beach. Priced competitively, this meticulously maintained home is an irresistible opportunity for any first-time home buyers, secondary residence, investment property, or relocation home! Act quickly, as this well-priced property is poised for a quick sale!
